Nicha Yontararak (Thai: ณิชา ยนตรรักษ์; born (1997-10-23)October 23, 1997), better known by her nickname and stage name Minnie (Korean: 민니; Thai: มินนี่), is a Thai singer, songwriter and actress based in South Korea.
She is a member of South Korean girl group (G)I-dle, which debuted on May 2, 2018 under Cube Entertainment.
